Reasoning: 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the most likely category as the paper deals with privacy and sanitisation of sensitive data. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is also likely as the paper discusses a database containing the data of multiple users. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses mutual information and differential privacy metrics to sanitise the dataset. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper discusses mutual information as a leakage metric. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is less likely but still possible as the paper mentions the computational complexity of finding optimal sanitisation protocols.
